          "html_url": "https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/commit/53f4743c2150d0ff10a4f7781e489131b8e030f3"
        }
      ],
      "message": "test: Allow to set height in create_block\n\nPreviously, it was only possible to set the height indirectly by calling\ncreate_coinbase outside the create_block function. This is fine, but\nverbose and not needed.\n\nJust like hashprev can be set directly (instead of using the value from\ntmpl), allow height to be set directly.\n\nAlso, use it in one place. The other places are done in a scripted-diff.",
      "committer": {
        "name": "MarcoFalke",
        "email": "*~=`'#}+{/-|&$^_@721217.xyz",
        "date": "2026-04-15T15:28:24Z"
      },
      "author": {
        "name": "MarcoFalke",
        "email": "*~=`'#}+{/-|&$^_@721217.xyz",
        "date": "2026-04-15T14:59:29Z"
